{"id":"melchi","term":"Melchi","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>My king. (1.) The son of Addi, and father of Neri (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 3:28\">Luke 3:28</a>). (2.) <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Luke 3:24\">Luke 3:24</a>.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Luke 3:28","Luke 3:24"]}